Allan,

Long (16-bit) forward DBRAs were also similarly broken.  Here are my
diffs, relative to the original sources I eloped with in October.  (You
DID keep a copy of those, didn't you?) There's some extra (probably
ignorable) cruft for my port to the 3B1 -- I hope you're not offended. 

I sincerely hope this stomps the last of the "forward reference out of
range" bugs, but I doubt it.  Care to try more test cases?


-Landon




